        <subsection xml:id="overview-converters">
          <title>Description</title>
          <p>The ship has two General Electric MV7306 propulsion converters, one for each propulsion motor.  The converters include the three main components shown in <xref ref="VFD_main_components"/>, as well as other supporting components housed in a row of cabinets located in converter rooms 1 and 2, on the 4th deck. The converters operate at extremely dangerous high voltages, so these rooms are normally locked and off-limits to all unauthorized personnel.</p>
